{"tid":1625728,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[開放討論] 究竟需唔需要星期六日兩日都有大型活動？","createTime":"2019-10-05T08:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T08:09:26.000Z","uid":319568,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ab43ff415f5725ce111a95141edba18fe59ddb4c","tid":1625728,"uid":319568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:04:31.000Z","msg":"兩日都有嘅話嘅好處<br />\n1. Keep住有人討論事件<br />\n2. 增加政府管治成本 <br />\n3. 可以消耗狗隻體力<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n揀一日有大型活動嘅好處<br />\n1. 大家可以有更多時間嘅休息，因為呢個係長期戰爭<br />\n2. 文宣組有時間做文宣<br />\n3. 有時間去醞釀發生左嘅事<br />\n4. 減少活動可以減少被捕人數<br />\n5. 可以更集中人數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人認為<br />\n因為呢場運動要贏嘅話<br />\n起碼係要支共倒台<br />\nwhich mean 就一定係長期戰爭+八國聯軍<br />\n所以個人建議<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">除非有重大事件</span></span><br />\n可以係平日（唔需要五日，可能一兩日就足夠）+ weekend 其中一日就夠<br />\n等文宣組有多d時間去準備<br />\n大家有多d時間同國際社會解釋<br />\n<br />\n大家唔需要太衝動<br />\n呢場運動未咁快到end game <br />\n支共一日唔倒台一日香港都唔會有好日子過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 兩日<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：一日"},{"pid":"17fc5eae169bf609663ee4d45d81a431959e4bc3","tid":1625728,"uid":319568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"p 牌推唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4dc6dfa7e79be54fd0031c2a317fbb282aa527","tid":1625728,"uid":319568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac